TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.FCST_SKU_KEY,FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.STYLE_NUM,FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.COLOR_CODE,FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.ATTRIBUTION_CODE,FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.SIZE_CODE FROM FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT WHERE FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.SBU_PRIMARY_IND = 'Y' AND FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.PROCESS_IND = 'N'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Join Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: APS_STYLE_CODE = STYLE_NUM AND APS_COLOR_CODE = COLOR_CODE AND APS_ATTRIBUTE_CODE = ATTRIBUTION_CODE AND APS_SIZE_CODE = SIZE_CODE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT HBI_DEMAND.APS_STYLE_CODE,HBI_DEMAND.APS_COLOR_CODE,HBI_DEMAND.APS_ATTRIBUTE_CODE,HBI_DEMAND.APS_SIZE_CODE FROM HBI_DEMAND HBI_DEMAND WHERE HBI_DEMAND.DEMAND_TYPE = 'CUSTOMERORDER'
